Welcome to Din Tai Fung,
home of the world-famous
Xiao Long Bao
(Steamed Dumplings)
Each Xiao Long Bao is created with surgical
precision, passing through a 40-minute
process of six different stations of hand
preparation before being served.
小笼包
Food Allergies & Intolerances
Guests with allergies or intolerances are advised to inform our service team before placing orders for food or
beverages. Guests with severe allergies or intolerances should be aware that although all due care is taken,
due to shared cooking and preparation areas, there is a risk of allergen ingredients still being present.
